>\n原來條友痴撚線架</strong><br />\n<br />\n無端白事俾人人身攻擊<br />\n幾日覺得唔啱梗係走㗎啦<br />\n唔通做咗兩個月先同你講話唔啱咩<br />\n你自己都要搵人頂替<br />\n都嗰時走咪仲仆街！？"},{"pid":"92d3aa76d16bbc7149eddf78a280a70d544e418c","tid":2059314,"uid":77369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T23:43:20.000Z","msg":"大家有無遇過咁既老闆/上司"},{"pid":"6826045a11b37af7b119c2d47119d7eb7ec44579","tid":2059314,"uid":46309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T23:44:16.000Z","msg":"唔駛理佢都戇撚鳩"},{"pid":"b42551fd21abf85ce0b21026c4f80d98550a8466","tid":2059314,"uid":77369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6826045a11b37af7b119c2d47119d7eb7ec44579","tid":2059314,"uid":46309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T23:44:16.000Z","msg":"唔駛理佢都戇撚鳩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T23:50:38.000Z","msg":"身邊好多朋友都話同佢講咁多真係戇鳩<br />\n真接拎番d野走<br />\n但以佢性格聽日一定捉住我黎罵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要講英文，淨係諗到fuck you想同佢講"}]}